CHANGELOG

v0.3
====

 RELEASE DATE: 2019-09-02

 Added support for exactly one theme "pink". Themes are stored in .bclrc,
 located at the root of this repo. Activate this theme by using the following
 one liner:

   $ echo pink > .bclrc

 Disable this theme using the following one liner:

   $ echo default > .bclrc

v0.2
====

 RELEASE DATE: 2019-09-02
 
 Added a variable to squash all of the command line arguments so that when the
 script is called, arguments will be passed to bettercap.


